      "description": "Hey there! I am so incredibly excited to share this absolute gem with you! Honestly, this car is in such gorgeous, pristine shape that it looks like it just rolled right off the showroom floor. It\u2019s been pampered and loved since day one, and it drives like an absolute dream. If you've been looking for a ride that's basically flawless and ready for a new home, this is the one! You really have to see it in person to believe how clean it is. Feel free to reach out with any questions\u2014I'd love to help you get behind the wheel of this beauty!",
