    },
    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Available is an investment-grade 2004 BMW M3, a masterclass in naturally aspirated performance. At its heart lies the S54 3.2L inline-six, featuring individual throttle bodies and a high-pressure VANOS system that delivers linear power up to an 8,000 RPM redline. Power is managed through a precise Getrag six-speed manual gearbox and a factory limited-slip differential. This example is mechanically pristine, with a reinforced rear subframe and a comprehensive service history ensuring peak structural and powertrain integrity. The exterior retains its deep luster with zero imperfections, while the cabin's Nappa leather remains supple and wear-free. This is a rare opportunity to own a mechanically synchronized E46 in showroom-fresh state.",
      "price": 46500.0,
      "reputation": 0.8,
