      "description": "Experience automotive perfection with this showroom-condition masterpiece. This vehicle has been meticulously maintained in a climate-controlled environment, preserving its flawless factory finish and deep, mirror-like luster. Inside, the cabin remains in a time-capsule state; the premium leather still carries that new-car aroma, entirely free from creases or wear. Every button, switch, and electronic feature operates with tactile precision. Mechanically, it is beyond reproach, boasting a documented service history with no expense spared. With incredibly low mileage and a spotless pedigree, this car offers the rare opportunity to own a vehicle that looks and drives exactly as it did the day it left the assembly line. Truly a collector-grade example for the most discerning driver.",
      "price": 46500.0,
